net.conquiris.schema
Interface UUIDSchemaItem

All Superinterfaces:
FieldNameProperty, IsIndexedFlag, IsStoredFlag, SchemaItem, TextSchemaItem
public interface UUIDSchemaItem
extends TextSchemaItem

Marker interface for UUID schema items. UUID schema items are considered ids, so they are not tokenized and have no norms and no vectors.

Author:
Andres Rodriguez
